## Population pyramid shapes (memorize these)

| Pyramid shape | DTM stage | What it means |
|---|---|---|
| **Wide base, narrow top** | Stage 2 | High birth rate, falling death rate, fast growth |
| **Even pyramid** | Stage 3 | Birth rate declining, slower growth |
| **Column shape** | Stage 4 | Stable population, low birth and death rates |
| **Inverted pyramid** | Stage 5 | Birth rate below death rate, declining population |

